         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">22/12/92. ¶  ¶ Let me express my best thanks, dear Mr Tepper, for the friendly feelings that you keep for me and which you again show through your felicitation for the approaching festival. ¶  ¶ May t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">92.12.22b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">22/12/92.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Lassen Sie meinen besten Dank ausgesprochen sein, lieber Herr Tepper, für die freundlichen Gefühle, welche Sie mir bewahren u welche Sie durch Ihre Felicitation zum jetzt kommenden Feste wieder bekundigen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Möge die neue annuelle Spanne Zeit, in welche wir nun bald hineinleben werden, auch für Sie und die Ihrigen sich als recht freudevoll erweisen!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Diesmal kann ich meinen Glückwunsch Owen, Quatrefages u Regel nicht mehr darbringen, u vielleicht bin ich der Erste nun, den die göttliche Versehung abruft!</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hoffentlich kann ich im nächsten Sept dort sein, und mich des Zusammenkommens auch mit Ihnen erfreuen!</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">22/12/92.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me express my best thanks, dear Mr Tepper, for the friendly feelings that you keep for me and which you again show through your felicitation for the approaching festival.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May the new span of time in which we now soon will live also prove to be very joyful for you and yours.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This time I can no longer offer my congratulations to Owen, Quatrefages and Regel,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">All three died in 1892: Quatrefages on 12 January, Regel on 27 April and Owen on 18 December.</p>
               </note> and perhaps I am now the first whom Providence will call away!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is to be hoped I can be there next September and also enjoy meeting with you!<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The 5th Congress of the Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science was to be held in Adelaide in September 1893.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
